        "title": "Require multipart package publishes",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Require `multipart/form-data` for `POST /api/v1/packages` and reject JSON package publish bodies before publish actions run.\n- Keep package artifact metadata server-created by rejecting public `artifact` payloads and splitting public/server package publish schemas.\n- Preserve multipart file and ClawPack publish paths, including documented `files[]` uploads, and update docs/spec coverage.\n\n## Tests\n\n- `bun run format:check`\n- `bun run lint`\n- `bun run test -- convex/httpApiV1.handlers.test.ts convex/packages.public.test.ts src/__tests__/plugins-publish-route.test.tsx packages/schema/src/schemas.test.ts`\n- `bun run --cwd packages/clawhub test:src -- src/cli/commands/packages.test.ts src/cli/commands/publish.test.ts src/http.test.ts src/http.bun.test.ts`\n- `bunx tsc -p packages/schema/tsconfig.json --noEmit`\n- `bunx tsc -p packages/clawhub/tsconfig.json --noEmit`\n- `bun run --cwd packages/schema build`\n- `bun run --cwd packages/clawhub verify`\n\n## Notes\n\n- `bunx tsc --noEmit` was attempted. It is blocked locally by worktree dependency layout after restoring the missing declared `@faker-js/faker` package: Vite plugin types resolve from both this worktree and the sibling checkout `node_modules` path.\n",
